    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-如果遇到了什么问题或者有什么好的建议，欢迎联系开发者</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-游戏目前仍在开发阶段，目标是创造PC平台最好的海军沙盒类游戏，如果你喜欢NavalArt，欢迎访问开发者的爱发电  或者 Patreon  来赞助开发并获得奖励 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-加入我们的官方Discord  或者贴吧来下载mod和获取游戏最新信息，让我们一起让NavalArt变得更加好玩  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏介绍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-《NavalArt》是一款拟合了建造，设计，物理，战斗于一身的单机模拟沙盒游戏，在游戏过程中，玩家将分别扮演设计船舰的工程师与参与战斗的指挥官,设计属于自己的独一无二的战舰，在钢铁与巨炮的时代指挥作战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-游戏中，玩家将以上帝视角在船坞中设计战舰。战舰的零件来自零件列表或者mod，玩家将其放置在指定位置，从而完成战舰的设计，大至整个船体，小到一根锚链。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/842780/extras/8a16c351d2bdf5a958004d9d3efd4e2d.poster.avif?t=1761013908\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/842780/extras/8a16c351d2bdf5a958004d9d3efd4e2d.webm?t=1761013908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/842780/extras/8a16c351d2bdf5a958004d9d3efd4e2d.mp4?t=1761013908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-舰船的各项参数至关重要，不同的防护和武器布局将会起到不同的效果，在试航场景下测试您的战舰，直到获得满意的设计。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/842780/extras/4d84f1c6cc5e62580f1d9d453566a7f2.poster.avif?t=1761013908\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/842780/extras/4d84f1c6cc5e62580f1d9d453566a7f2.webm?t=1761013908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/842780/extras/4d84f1c6cc5e62580f1d9d453566a7f2.mp4?t=1761013908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-在战役和快速战斗模式中，使用多种火力强大的武器，例如鱼雷和穿甲弹，指挥您的舰队获得胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/842780/extras/de4ceadafc9caee991695c62ffe5d5d8.poster.avif?t=1761013908\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/842780/extras/de4ceadafc9caee991695c62ffe5d5d8.webm?t=1761013908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/842780/extras/de4ceadafc9caee991695c62ffe5d5d8.mp4?t=1761013908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-使用包括密集阵在内的防空武器武装你的船只，在试航场景的空袭中存活下来吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/842780/extras/fcf70eacfc8760fdfade011fbfa60e27.poster.avif?t=1761013908\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/842780/extras/fcf70eacfc8760fdfade011fbfa60e27.webm?t=1761013908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/842780/extras/fcf70eacfc8760fdfade011fbfa60e27.mp4?t=1761013908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-想体验船员的感觉吗，没有问题，在画廊模式下，玩家可以检阅自己的整个舰队，并且在甲板之上漫步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/842780/extras/f0e9ed72ed31166eb0b1f08f2521698e.poster.avif?t=1761013908\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/842780/extras/f0e9ed72ed31166eb0b1f08f2521698e.webm?t=1761013908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/842780/extras/f0e9ed72ed31166eb0b1f08f2521698e.mp4?t=1761013908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-对于设计没有头绪, 想要更多的零件？不要忘记访问我们的创意工坊来获得海量的战舰设计 (当然，不局限于舰船) 和mod！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/842780/extras/20f41c2f28a8f11e3ef51cf86cdbc252.poster.avif?t=1761013908\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/842780/extras/20f41c2f28a8f11e3ef51cf86cdbc252.webm?t=1761013908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/842780/extras/20f41c2f28a8f11e3ef51cf86cdbc252.mp4?t=1761013908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·基于历史的装备</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·大量战役</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·水下视角</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·包括海浪的实时物理计算</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·不同天气与昼夜变换</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·快速战斗模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·画廊模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·防空武器系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·潜艇系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·Mod支持</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·创意工坊设计分享</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·创意工坊Mod安装</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·基于Steam的多人游戏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·密集阵，导弹等现代武器</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >未来将会加入</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·航空母舰</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·历史任务</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·任务编辑器</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·更多地图</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·更多部件 (包括密集阵，导弹等现代武器)</p>",
